parameters:
What the hell is this!? This ridiculous outfit!
Change it back right now!

You seem to be quite the troublemaker, so we've
modified you to be more obedient. It suits you
well.

How is it, you can't resist, can you? We're
controlling your body with the device attached to
your prosthetic.

Ugh! I won't just let you guys have your way with
me...!

Oh, as expected of a cyborg, such incredible
strength... But... Sit.

My body is moving on its own...! I'll never
forgive you for this...!

This is a complete disgrace. If the auction venue
is exposed, we'll have to change the location and
postpone it. The losses would be incalculable.
Serves you right! It's what you deserve!

To cover the losses, we're going to market you as
a humanoid dog robot. Today, you'll be doing some
advertising for us.
Don't mess with me! You scumbags!
You guys, bring that over here.
Hey! What do you think you're doing!?

Gyahahaha! I'm going to shove this into your
bladder now.

Gyahahaha! Well, we can't neglect to take the
doggy for a walk!

No, there's no way it can be done in this state,
right⁉

Now, let's take the doggy out for a walk~ We have
to show the townsfolk what happens when they
oppose the Empire.
How terrible... Is that the Resistance...?

It's because they opposed the Empire, they got
what they deserved.

You're quite popular! Try wagging your tail and
greet them.
Now, let's move on to the next location.
(Ugh... hurry up... this is the worst...)

(I need to hold it together... I can't let
myself... wet myself... in front of these guys...)
Well then, shall we take a smoke break?

Well, well, don't get so worked up. You're shaking
like a Chihuahua.
(Ahh, no, no more! I can't take it anymore!)

Hey, hey, if you're going to pee, do it like a
dog.

Reacting to the Imperial Soldier's words, Esuka's
prosthetic limb jerked upwards.

Ah... Aaaaah! Not like this! Not in front of these
guys!
Gyahahaha! What a poorly trained little dog!
How cruel. Don't they have any human pride?

The walks with the Imperial Soldier were repeated
several times after that for Esuka.
